OL,5,G1250 Heartbeat
OL,6,     FMembers of the local constabulary
OL,7,     Fpatrol the town of Ashfordly and
OL,8,     Fthe nearby village of Aidensfield,
OL,9,     Fkeeping the peace whilst also
OL,10,     Fdealing with local loveable
OL,11,     Frogues.
OL,12,G1355 My Unique B&B
OL,13,     FAll around the country lie unique
OL,14,     Fspaces, in beautiful places:
OL,15,     Fcampervans; sheds, attics;
OL,16,     Fcaravans even horseboxes! They are
OL,17,     Funloved and unused. . . until now!
